    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>50个精彩关卡，等你来挑战!!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192390/extras/9e8d4d7c1681d4aa4a764275b1f7a23d.poster.avif?t=1762307614\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192390/extras/9e8d4d7c1681d4aa4a764275b1f7a23d.webm?t=1762307614\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192390/extras/9e8d4d7c1681d4aa4a764275b1f7a23d.mp4?t=1762307614\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >世界的玛那濒临枯竭，错觉之都「米拉渚」即将面临崩塌的危机！带领酷博德破解 50 个视觉谜题，阻止米拉渚的末日降临！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>挑战大脑极限的谜题机制！！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192390/extras/1dbe6ec0ca6b1077db5a6940a0b025d2.poster.avif?t=1762307614\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192390/extras/1dbe6ec0ca6b1077db5a6940a0b025d2.webm?t=1762307614\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192390/extras/1dbe6ec0ca6b1077db5a6940a0b025d2.mp4?t=1762307614\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一关都挑战你的感知能力，迫使你从不同的角度看待这个世界。立方体的移动考验着你在狭小空间中的空间推理和问题解决能力。利用视角的力量，穿越不可能的地形。但要小心，一步失误，全盘重来！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>五种不同的环境等你探索！！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192390/extras/c85e4289ae0d19093914471d6ed9599a.poster.avif?t=1762307614\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192390/extras/c85e4289ae0d19093914471d6ed9599a.webm?t=1762307614\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192390/extras/c85e4289ae0d19093914471d6ed9599a.mp4?t=1762307614\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >带着酷博德探索 5 种不同的环境，享受令人惊叹、色彩丰富的风格化景观。每个环境都有其独特的特点，确保你的冒险旅程始终充满新鲜感！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>巧妙利用道具，解开难题！！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192390/extras/893e019339f47f5f450e83b91ca0f8f5.poster.avif?t=1762307614\" width=600 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192390/extras/893e019339f47f5f450e83b91ca0f8f5.webm?t=1762307614\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192390/extras/893e019339f47f5f450e83b91ca0f8f5.mp4?t=1762307614\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一些障碍可能看起来难以克服。仔细看看周围的环境以及你手中的道具，也许解决方案早就在你眼前！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>挑战自己的最佳成绩！！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192390/extras/2b23ae001626066e4aac3f4ded00e3ff.poster.avif?t=1762307614\" width=600 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192390/extras/2b23ae001626066e4aac3f4ded00e3ff.webm?t=1762307614\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192390/extras/2b23ae001626066e4aac3f4ded00e3ff.mp4?t=1762307614\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >觉得自己能超越自我？想炫耀自己的效率？挑战自己，打破之前的记录！</p>",
